                        <span class="tei-persName"> Bar Nbyl </span>
                    </span>
                </span> <a href="/793-11" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><h4>Birth: </h4><p class="indent"><span class="spearLabel">Birth place: </span><span class="tei-persName">Bar
                                    Nbyl</span> came from a village called <span class="tei-placeName">Fytr</span>.  <a href="/793-7" class="factoid-more"> See factoid page <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><h4>Occupation(s): </h4><p class="indent"><span class="tei-persName">Bar Nbyl</span>
                                was archimandrite at <span class="tei-placeName">the monastery in <span class="tei-placeName">Fytr</span></span>.  <a href="/793-9" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p></div><div class="sources"><h3>Relationships</h3><p class="indent"> Bar Nbyl  was a follower of
                                 Mara Dada . <a href="/793-10" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><p class="indent">Habib was a
                            follower of  Bar Nbyl . <a href="/793-4" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p></div><div class="sources"><h3>Events</h3><p class="indent">Bar Nbyl
                            planted the monastery in Fytr.  <a href="/793-13" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><hr/><p class="indent"> When Habib was 10 years old, he entered the monastery in Fytr,
                            under the direction of Bar Nbyl.  <a href="/793-14" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><hr/><p class="indent"> After Bar
                            Nbyl lived 90 years, he died, leaving the monastery in Fytr to
                                Habib.
                         <a href="/793-15" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><hr/></div><div class="citation"><h3>How to cite:</h3><span class="element">
